<div class="about-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: '100%', alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
          <div class="skill">
            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            <div class="progress">

              <div
                class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                role="progressbar"
                style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                aria-valuemax="100">
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>I currently reside in Somerset West. I have a Bachelors degree in Biodiversity and Ecology and am a self-taught software developer. My current interest is in website design and I specialize in Ruby on Rails. </p>

