              Somerset-West
              <br>
              2006  – June 2008
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Somerset Private School
              <br>
              July 2008 – December 2010
              <br>
              <%= link_to 'National Senior Certificate', "https://personal-documents-bucket.s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com/PJ+de+Villiers+-+National+Senior+Certificate.PDF" %>
              Additional Subjects:
              <br>
              Mathematics P3 (78%)
              <br>
              Psychology AS-Level (Passed)
              <br>
              Stellenbosch Entrance Examination (70%)

